		{"id":"a4ebddab76f09817","type":"text","text":"![[Pasted image 20241204133230.png]]\n\n这里的**薄片型物体**表明 $S$ 是一个曲面, 因此第二问应该是曲面积分.\n\n1. 先求方程, 代入 $z^2=2x$\n$$\n\\left\\{\\begin{align}&z=\\sqrt{ x^2+y^2 } \\\\\n&z^2=2x\n\\end{align}\\right. \\implies (x-1)^2+y^2 = 1\n$$\n2. $S$ 的质量\n$$\nM=\\iint_{\\sum} 9\\sqrt{ x^2+y^2+z^2 }dS\n$$\n其中\n$$\nz'_{x}=\\dfrac{x}{\\sqrt{ x^2+y^2 }},z'_{y} =\\dfrac{y}{\\sqrt{ x^2+y^2 }},dS=\\sqrt{ 1+(z'_{x})^2+(z'_{y})^2 }dxdy = \\sqrt{ 2 }dxdy\n$$\n故\n$$\nM=18\\iint_{D}\\sqrt{ x^2+y^2 }dxdy = 36 \\int^{\\dfrac{\\pi}{2}}_{0} \\int^{2\\cos \\theta}_{0}r^2 dr d\\theta = 64\n$$","x":1960,"y":1803,"width":1140,"height":837},
